    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei salvatoris Iesu Christi. Nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/186"
                            >Sicardus</persName>, Dei providencia, Beneventane provincie <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, per rogum <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/1905"
                            >Roffrid</persName>, <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">referendarii</rs>
                        nostri, firmamus in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Churches #Landed_possessions #Slave_labour #Slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1900">Beatissimi Vincencii</orgName>, ubi
                        venerabilis vir <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1903"
                            >Epyphanius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>, orator noster, preesse videtur, <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/1903"
                            >Sancti Secundini</orgName>, cum integris suis <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">pertinenciis</rs>, <rs key="#Fines"
                            >finibus</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines #Churches #Landed_possessions" ref="#estates/1907"
                            >Acerentinis</geogName>, quam <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/1904">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> per suam<rs key="#Offersio/donatio">
                            offercionem</rs> ibidem dedit; seu et confirmamus in predicto cenobio
                            <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >substanciam</rs>
                        <persName key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannis</name></persName> et <persName key="#Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Radoaldus">Radoaldi</name></persName>, filii <persName><name
                                ref="Pico">Piconis</name></persName>; et substanciam <persName
                            key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Ermelgrimus"
                            >Ermelgrimi</name></persName>, filio <persName><name ref="Ratepertus"
                                >Rapperti</name></persName>; tam et <persName
                            key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Stephanus"
                            >Stephani</name></persName>, filii <persName><name ref="Paldo"
                                >Paldonis</name></persName>; simulque et <persName
                            key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Truppoaldus"
                            >Truppoaldi</name></persName>, filii <persName><name ref="Andreas"
                                >Andree</name></persName>; quam et substaticiam <persName
                            key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Ragibertus"
                            >Ragimberti</name></persName>, <persName key="#Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Radoaldus">Radoald</name></persName>, filii <persName><name
                                ref="Radipertus">Radiperti</name></persName>; et substanciam
                            <persName key="#Landed_possessions"><name ref="Trasmundus"
                                >Trasemundi</name></persName>, filio <persName><name ref="Lupinus"
                                >Lupini</name></persName>, que vestro monasterio date sunt; simulque
                        inibi confirmamus omnes <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Slave_labour #Slave"
                            >servos et ancillas</rs> eorum, cum filiis, filiabus, cum nuris et
                        nepotibus, et cum universis cespitibus eorum in iam dicto monasterio
                        confirmamus, omnia possidenda in integrum, qualiter pro culpa, meritis
                        eorum, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Inflow #Inheritance #Confiscation"
                            >ad sacrum nostrum palacium evenire</rs> debuerunt. in ea videlicet
                        racione, ut a modo et deinceps, per hoc nostrum roboratum preceptum, cuncta,
                        ut superius leguntur, rectores eiusdem cenobii securiter habere et possidere
                        valeant, et a nullis ex nostris iudicibus, idest comitibus, gastaldeis, vel
                        a quibuscumque agentibus habeant aliquam requisicionem, sed perpetuis
                        temporibus possideant. Quod vero preceptum firmitatis, ex iussione
                        suprascripte potestatis, scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Leo"
                                >Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Palatium"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName>, in <rs key="#Palatium">sacro
                            palacio</rs>, primo anno, mense augusto, undecima indiccione,
                        feliciter.</ab>
